flowchart TD
    A[New Alert] --> B{Severity?}
    B -->|info| Z[Skip triage]
    B -->|warning / critical| C[Start triage agent]
    C --> D[Query correlated alerts]
    D --> E[Look up host info]
    E --> F[Search runbooks]
    F --> G{Assessment}
    G -->|low risk| H[Classify: noise / acknowledged]
    G -->|needs tracking| I[Create incident]
    G -->|critical, multi-alert| J[Create incident + escalate]
    I --> K[Return triage result]
    J --> K
    H --> K
    K --> L[Stream result to dashboard]
